TopicTitle: Part Packs Based on Historical or Present Spacecraft [Non-stock]

Articles.Content:
Listing of Mods/Part Packs (Alphabetical)

Mod Name - System(s) Summary

[BobCat's Historical Spacecraft](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/81754-Release-BobCat-Ind-Space-Planet-products) - Soviet Engines, Soyuz, Progess, MIR, Lunokhod, Kliper, Proton, N1, Buran Shuttle, Orion, Ares I, Ares V

[Component Space Shuttle](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/121748-Component-Space-Shuttle-CSS-ksp-1-0-2-unofficial-release-thread) - Space Shuttle

[Chaka Monkey](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/64993) - Orion, SLS, MLS, EMLV

[FASA](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/27/FASA) - Pioneer, Explorer, Mercury/Redstone/Atlas, Gemini/Atlas, Apollo/Saturn, Nova

[KOSMOS URM](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/323/KOSMOS%20URM%20Package) - URM-1 Angara

[Launchers Pack](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/157/Launchers%20Pack) - Atlas V, Delta II, Falcon 1, 

[LazTek SpaceX](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/29388) - Dragon, Falcon 9, Falcon Heavy, SHERPA

[Proton 8K82K(M)](http://www.curse.com/ksp-mods/kerbal/220464-ussr-proton-8k82k-m) - Proton Rocket

[N-1 (11A52)](http://www.curse.com/ksp-mods/kerbal/220466-n-1) - N-1 Rocket

[Salyut Stations & Soyuz](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/79) - Vostok, Voskhod, Salyut, Soyuz, Progress

[Skylab](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/50/Skylab) - Skylab

[Soviet Probes & Rockets](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/75/Soviet%20Probes%20%26%20Rockets) - Progress Block L, Luna 9, Luna 10, Molniya-1, Luna 2, Sputnik 1-3, Voskhod, Vostok, Proton

[SNC Dreamchaser](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/267/Dreamer%20-%20SNC%20Dream%20Chaser) - DreamChaser, Atlas V, Centaur

[Space Factory](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/47765-Space-Factory) - Voskhod-2, Angara, Vostok, Luna-17

[Tantares](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/303/Tantares%20-%20Stockalike%20Soyuz%20%26%20More) - Soyuz, Progress, Salyut, TKS, Cygnus, ATV, MIR, Vostok

[Tantares LV](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/362/Tantares%20LV%20-%20Stockalike%20Proton%20%26%20More) - Proton, R-7 (Soyuz-FG), Ariane 5, Antares Rocket, Castor Upper Stage, N-1, V-2

[US Probe Pack](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/158/US%20Probes%20Pack%20-%20Old%20and%20New) - Pioneer, EOS sats, NEO sats, Galileo, Magellan, TDRS, MESSENGER, Vanguard, Dawn, Deep Impact, Deep Space 1, NEAR, Stardust, Ulysses, IUS Booster, PAM, Tiros, GRAB, TransitA, Explorer

Just to name a few... If I have missed any of your favorite mods, please let me know and I will update the list.
